             Greeceâ€™s Finance Ministry said it is
studying an offer by Piraeus Bank SA to acquire the stakes the
state owns in Agricultural Bank of Greece SA and Hellenic
Postbank SA.  
 The offer is being considered in the light of public
interest and the prospects of the specific banks as well as the
